summary: Makes the Slaughterfish stop attacking you in water!
descriptionHtml:
Ever thought that those pesky slaughterfish were uber annoying as there is no combat in water. I do... So I made this mod that pretty much makes the slaughterfish not attack in water as well as having no damage. Ive added the fact that Slaughterfish are now non-hostile. So that should be right now! 

However I am unsure if it has any major bugs I cant find any.
author: tomycins
